19:09.481 --> 19:11.400
'cause there's no way to know
what's in the guy's head,

19:11.483 --> 19:13.443
a white guy laughing a little too hard.

19:13.527 --> 19:16.155
And at that moment,
he's like, "What am I doing?"

19:16.238 --> 19:20.159
And it's that precise moment
of vulnerability,

19:20.242 --> 19:23.412
it's like, if you want to walk
to that fence and deal with it,

19:23.495 --> 19:24.830
then you gotta be on the fence.

19:24.913 --> 19:26.957
Mmm-hmm.
-Fried chicken is kind of on that fence.

19:27.040 --> 19:28.333
Yeah. Yeah. You're right.

19:28.417 --> 19:31.253
In terms of
its socio

19:31.336 --> 19:34.882
Can you take the cultural history
