<i>Busy Bee is in a historically</i>
<i>black area of Atlanta,</i>

24:04.693 --> 24:06.236
<i>doing traditional soul food</i>

24:06.319 --> 24:09.447
<i>as you could imagine it being served,</i>
<i>say, 30 years ago.</i>

