<i>I knew that I wanted</i>
<i>to open a restaurant.</i>

26:44.602 --> 26:46.521
<i>Yeah, that was the goal. </i>

26:47.355 --> 26:52.110
<i>For me, it's been a hard road</i>
<i>in figuring out my identity as a chef,</i>

