No. I'm doing what represents what I feel
as a chef should be on my menu,

27:07.417 --> 27:10.795
and I wanted people
to experience that first and foremost.

27:11.338 --> 27:16.509
My French training, my Italian training
and my love for Southern cuisine.

27:16.593 --> 27:18.345
You know, if you're a Southern chef,
